query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-room',
'decorator',
'editor',
'export-to-excel',
'fetch',
'hbase',
'hiveql',
'html-email',
'imap',
'mono',
'ms-access-2010',
'resultset',
'reverse');
